I"_<p>A smooth sake that can be particularly enjoyed heated, with an umami that
blooms in the mouth. When heated to 50°C, you can enjoy the rich rice aroma.
Even when heated it retains its smoothness and clean finish, without any
bitterness developing.</p>

<p>Pairs well with seafood and poultry dishes.</p>

<p>Serve chilled or hot (around 50°C)</p>
